description.m_value: Absorbs shallow water to attack all allied melee units on the map, dealing splash damage in a cross; when on Blighted tiles, attacks deal additional <@eb.key>Arts damage</> and causes <@eb.key>Blight</> to the paddy

Takes up <@eb.key>3</> Block; Runs upon taking damage, significantly increasing <@eb.key>Movement Speed</> for a short time and dealing heavy damage to <@eb.key>Throttle Valves</> it passes over; <@eb.key>grants</> deployable unit when defeated
